on right click:
    if {banBedBomingOption} is "&aEnabled":
        if world of event-block contains "world_nether" or "world_the_end":
            if event-block is white bed, light gray bed, gray bed, black bed, brown bed, red bed, orange bed, yellow bed, lime bed, green bed, cyan bed, light blue bed, blue bed, purple bed, magenta bed or pink bed:
                cancel event
                send "&cBed bombing is disabled!" to player

